{"tid":2067950,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［獨派的最後時光］知唔知6月21係咩日子？係香港獨立日, HONG KONG INDEPENDENCE DAY","createTime":"2020-06-17T10:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T12:02:23.000Z","uid":258731,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"488c8670d6e65309730ad8636a7e7bfe11f2423e","tid":2067950,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T10:32:21.000Z","msg":"知唔知621係咩日子？<br />\n除咗係<br />\n係香港獨立日, HONG KONG INDEPENDENCE DAY<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨派而家最需要嘅係咩？<br />\n係一個屬於我哋嘅紀念日子<br />\n<br />\n點解係6.21？<br />\n中共黨安法壓境<br />\n佢最想就係7.1之前過到兼且可以開始實行<br />\n我哋要做嘅就係殺佢一個措手不及<br />\n先發制人<br />\n所以我哋獨派就係要係7.1之前做一個大型造勢運動<br />\n以後啲人記得香港紀念日，唔係7.1，而要係6.21<br />\n<br />\n6.21有咩做？<br />\n食黃店<br />\n做手勢<br />\n叫口號<br />\n繼續鳩叫<br />\n唔需要局限係屋企窗口，唔需要局限時間空間<br />\n有人嘅地方<br />\n商場，黨鐵月台，車廂<br />\n「民族自強，香港獨立」<br />\n「香港獨立，唯一出路」<br />\n「One Nation, One Hong Kong」<br />\n「香港人，建國」<br />\n<br />\n珍惜獨派仲可以係枱面上可以見光嘅日子<br />\n6.21，可能係你最後一次夠膽係公開場合叫香港獨立<br />\n6.21，可能係你最後一次夠膽係公開場合叫唱香港國歌願榮光<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p3oOUcZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp3oOUcZ.jpg&h=e421874f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xizVzdj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxizVzdj.jpg&h=fa57ce65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n6.21香港獨立日, HONG KONG INDEPENDENCE DAY<br />\n6.21香港獨立日, HONG KONG INDEPENDENCE DAY<br />\n6.21香港獨立日, HONG KONG INDEPENDENCE DAY<br />\n<br />\n因為好重要，所以要講三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5ea91893180069de0470150004f03b14dfa8966","tid":2067950,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:00:35.000Z","msg":"知唔知 620係咩日子<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">「每個人都應該喺自己嘅崗位上為推動民主出一分力。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n620罷工罷課公投<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JFWg3gr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJFWg3gr.jpg&h=bfe7a447&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9qxBBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9qxBBs.jpg&h=6da930b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C7JZ028.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC7JZ028.jpg&h=6c357510&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PvkNquP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPvkNquP.jpg&h=43c3bd09&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"56f8552d52a414f22aa31a7f2937ca982b8b055b","tid":2067950,"uid":201011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd1f5a07b665f8187dfc4b7c9e5eea8a9443d19f","tid":2067950,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T11:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb9ba5105304ba63217af91a4087ca9a10a34d1","tid":2067950,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T12:02:23.000Z","msg":"國旗ready<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}